{"tid":1285622,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"其實陳怡呢條友咩立埸","createTime":"2019-07-04T15:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T14:09:16.000Z","uid":253170,"like":5,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc641fbaed0523901da1a22ece06a4b09da717f","tid":1285622,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"睇佢#反佔中 既片 <br />\n從來冇直接表明自己政治立埸 (可能因為我冇睇哂)<br />\n絕大部份影片內容都係單純指罵廢青搞事<br />\n分化香港中年同青年人之外<br />\n深藍?柒藍?扮藍?愛國愛港?<br />\n<br />\n但原來除此之外<br />\n佢多年以黎都拍片侮辱親愛既內地同胞、內地文化、歌頌港英<br />\n一直都嘗試分化我地香港人同內地人<br />\n枉依家咁多愛港同胞支持陳怡 #反送中<br />\n<br />\n睇番以前既片 字字珠璣句句有力<br />\n我諗佢對香港被赤化 社會資源,文化比大陸人侵蝕既體會一定不淺<br />\n真心想知點解咁憎大陸人大陸文化點解會變成依家咁<br />\n更加confused究竟佢係咩人<br />\n愛中共?憎大陸?黃轉藍?扮藍? <br />\nor maybe just an attention seeker<br />\n<br />\n希望佢唔會DELETE 以前你拍既片<br />\nBTW有冇人識backup youtube片<br />\n<br />\n香港人質素愈來愈差的真正原因<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PkgoC2nBtaY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPkgoC2nBtaY&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=a65401fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PkgoC2nBtaY</a><br />\n以前的香港🇬🇧 今天的香港🇭🇰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xe9WfTn1zrg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXe9WfTn1zrg&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=b8701bc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xe9WfTn1zrg</a><br />\n香港的大陸西🍉 Mainlanders in Hong Kong<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x74lJHO4XgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx74lJHO4XgI&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=7f57f90e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x74lJHO4XgI</a><br />\n認真談談大陸西<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VvYiXdGB8yA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%